name.k: アングリーバード 2 (Angry Birds 2)

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 人気のクラシックなスリングショットアクション鳥ゲーム !

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It took less than a minute for us to get hooked on this series all over again. The sequel to Rovio’s blockbuster puzzler polishes the feathery fun to a golden sheen—and with more than just beautiful new graphics. Features like multi-stage levels, pig-punishing spells and choosing the order in which you fling birds make the game more irresistible than ever. Whether it’s your first Angry Birds game or your 10th, you’ll be flying high in no time.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 火藥味十足的動物對決再次回歸，拉滿弓向邪惡的偷蛋豬展開襲擊！
